description: Standalone git command line tool powered by js-git and node.js. Created to get rid of local git dependency in npm and bower, so contains only tiny subset of git features for those tools.
releaseNotes:
- added Node.js 0.12/4/5 support
- added npm 2/3 support
- added checkout exact commits support
- various fixes
- [nuget] user PATH is not automatically updated anymore
summary: Local git replacement for npm and bower, powered by js-git and node.js.
